82.04.050
definition of retail sale;

Digital goods, digital codes, and digital automated services, if the sale is included within the RCW
82.04.050
definition of retail sale;

Services, other than digital automated services, included within the RCW
82.04.050
definition of retail sale;

Off-road vehicles as defined in RCW
46.04.365
;

The rates provided in this section apply to taxes imposed under chapter
82.12
RCW as provided in RCW
82.12.020
